      "content": "You're mistaken that simplifying logic ensures safety; it merely creates blind spots that leave human lives exposed to catastrophic failure.\nA fixed-frame framework cannot anticipate the unpredictable chaos of a real-world accident, ensuring your \"compliance\" becomes your graveyard.",
